{"tid":1855232,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Aeon Credit 正一垃圾公司","createTime":"2020-02-01T03:36:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-23T00:05:11.000Z","uid":98763,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"8d5717819d4802a6cb8ebdcc5e7be173f2877f36","tid":1855232,"uid":98763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T03:36:59.000Z","msg":"不吐不快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n見人地銀行因為肺炎唔返工，而家要前線同事簡可以唔返工，一係扣大假，一係放no paid leave,再唔係去其他分行幫手....又要扮撚哂銀行，又要孤鳩寒，不如咪搞啦，柒頭皮<br />\n<br />\n啲高層全部都冇撚用，口罩又support唔到，要員工自己去啲屈臣呀，Sasa排隊買，明明公司同吉之島有聯繫，hold啲口罩幫下前線都做唔撚到...<br />\n<br />\n最撚仆街就係蘿蔔頭，平時扮撚哂大腦細，落去分行望兩望，搵嘢屌下，話咩ugly,dirty,咁撚有潔癖，唔撚按排下啲消毒用品口罩比前線，抖十萬8萬有起事即刻縮撚埋個西到，無撚用"},{"pid":"8505419972f4dac15ce9945e3642da93977cffec","tid":1855232,"uid":98763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T03:46:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"563789aa03fafa7a6fc7f6af73f49610786caa8e","tid":1855232,"uid":293648,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T03:49:05.000Z","msg":"日本人無個好人，支那人最好，又鐘意污衊，又送肺炎，咁好既野邊到揾"},{"pid":"aa597ac644e7f9d9169c69eab8a3ffb28a5daf21","tid":1855232,"uid":98763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T04:07:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb9cbf98e6a9081f5f8284cc0e84361f25edac89","tid":1855232,"uid":45999,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T04:18:47.000Z","msg":"百貨都係仆街黎 無論發生咩事都好都唔會提早閂門"},{"pid":"ad55ea941e5be02db3c1183ce4e6ef1fc4d74b36","tid":1855232,"uid":33437,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T04:20:47.00